 or freelancers, and other related expenses when\r\npreparing your budget</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhere you have an app built will also affect costs. There may be cheaper agencies outside of the United States, but it’s also important to keep quality\r\nand your feedback and communication structures in mind when making your choice. Follow this basic thought process when figuring out costs: initial mobile\r\napp design and development expenses + the “extras” mentioned above = your estimated costs.','they have in mind, or if it may be best to rethink their concept','','publish','open','open','','they-have-in-mind-or-if-it-may-be-best-to-rethink-their-concept','','','2019-01-26 09:30:45','2019-01-26 09:30:45','',0,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-hospital/?p=1421',0,'post','',0),(1422,1,'2019-01-23 06:48:38','2019-01-23 06:48:38','','slide3','','inherit','open','closed','','slide3','','','2019-01-23 06:48:38','2019-01-23 06:48:38','',1421,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-hospital/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/slide3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1424,1,'2019-01-23 10:12:55','2019-01-23 10:12:55','','favicon','','inherit','open','closed','','favicon','','','2019-01-23 10:12:55','2019-01-23 10:12:55','',0,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-hospital/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/favicon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1425,1,'2019-01-23 10:16:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-01-23 10:16:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-hospital/?p=1425',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1428,1,'2019-01-23 10:19:21','2019-01-23 10:19:21','','Dropdown','','publish','closed','closed','','dropdown','','','2019-01-23 11:05:26','2019-01-23 11:05:26','',0,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-hospital/?p=1428',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1429,1,'2019-01-23 11:05:26','2019-01-23 11:05:26',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1429','','','2019-01-23 11:05:26','2019-01-23 11:05:26','',0,'http://34.228.16.171/healing-touch-h